  <?dbhtml dir="tree"?>
  <title>SWT toolkit tree</title>
  <para>
  	A tree in SWT is essentially the same as a tree in Swing, with an extra option to have checkboxes on the nodes of the
  	tree. Use this component if you want to select or check the selection of checkboxes on an SWT tree. For other actions on
  	trees use the tree component in the <emphasis>concrete</emphasis> toolkit. 
  </para>
